  <brief_title>Study to Assess Safety, Tolerability and PK of AZD1480 in Patients With Solid Tumours</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase I, Open-Label, Multi-Center, Dose-Escalation Study to Assess the Safety and Tolerability, and Pharmacokinetics of AZD1480 Administered as Daily Oral Monotherapy in Patients With Advanced Solid Malignancies in the Escalation Phase and EGFR or ROS Mutant NSCLC or Non-Smokers With Lung Metastasis in the Expansion Phase.</official_title>
